Package Clinic.Server.Connection

Class AdaptableServer

java.lang.Object
Clinic.Server.Connection.AbstractServer
Clinic.Server.Connection.AdaptableServer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
class AdaptableServer
extends AbstractServer
The AdaptableServer is an adapter class that extends the AbstractServer class in place of the AbstractObservableServer .

Project Name: OCSF (Object Clinic.Client-Clinic.Server Framework)

Version:
Febuary 2001
Author:
Dr. Robert Laganière
